channel.title: --------->~~~~Massimo Server (BETA) project!~~~~<---------
channel.description:
Hello everyone.. this is my latest project.. and well i thought i would post some pics and what its like so far...
Well to start off...
--Server is only 67% done--
-Every skill works. -Membership (go on forums to learn more about it) -Specials -Vengeance -God wars -Full pking -Edge 1 vs 1 pking -Custom Client -Custom Items -working music player -new game frame. -new starting point -working pots -full teleports - and alot more...
This project is just a beta.. it hasnt been tested by anyone yet.. i used my other server A.M Explision to start out with..
Login screen-- [img]http://i38.tinypic.com/oa92zt.png[/img] Starting screen-- [img]http://i36.tinypic.com/2cnw6j9.png[/img] Starting point-- [img]http://i34.tinypic.com/2h83hwy.png[/img] Low training-- druids drop herblore stuff--- [img]http://i37.tinypic.com/2e6hs7l.png[/img] Shops-- [img]http://i37.tinypic.com/33oid1i.png[/img] Woodcutting-- [img]http://i34.tinypic.com/23j5u1v.png[/img] Full dragon (g)-- [img]http://i37.tinypic.com/t97i8z.png[/img] Dad and Veng-- [img]http://i35.tinypic.com/2eaifbt.png[/img] Slayer--- [img]http://i34.tinypic.com/os95yv.png[/img]
As i said.. the server is 67% done.. client 92% done... so post and tell me what you think... also vote and tell me if i should release server and client.
Thanks, ~Aaron~ "xstrxpurez"
